{"word":"G1586 - ἐκλέγομαι - eklégomai - ek-leg'-om-ahee - Make choice","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκλέγομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eklégomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-leg'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Make choice</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தெரிந்துகொள்"},{"paragraph":"to pick out, choose"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G3004 - λέγω - légō - leg'-o/3004\">G3004</a> (in its primary sense); to <i>select:</i> - make choice, choose (out), chosen.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1586/1586\">G1586</a>, <a href=\"#/G1588/1588\">G1588</a>, <a href=\"#/G1589/1589\">G1589</a>, <a href=\"#/G249/249\">G249</a>, <a href=\"#/G2980/2980\">G2980</a>, <a href=\"#/G3004/3004\">G3004</a>, <a href=\"#/G3050/3050\">G3050</a>, <a href=\"#/G3051/3051\">G3051</a>, <a href=\"#/G3052/3052\">G3052</a>, <a href=\"#/G3054/3054\">G3054</a>, <a href=\"#/G3055/3055\">G3055</a>, <a href=\"#/G3056/3056\">G3056</a>"}]}